title: MDSP-2: Shelter Proposal: Cayman Islands Humane Society
body:
Title:
VOTE for the Cayman Islands Humane Society (https://www.caymanislandshumanesociety.com/) as your shelter of choice for your interest! 

{Summary/ Plan A}
The Cayman Islands Humane Society is run by Crypto Conscious founders  who love ensuring cats and other animals find their home wether local or abroad. A leader in the Cayman Crypto Community has worked with the CIHS for years bringing animals back and forth from Canada and other places abroad. 

{Campaign Marketing}
Radio Cayman
Cayman Times
Cayman Press
Camana Bay Times
Breeze FM
Television / Movie Ad Marketing 

Cayman is warming up to crypto as more and more founders move to its beautiful shores. With over 1trillion dollars in value alone accounted for and companies like Brave, Chainlink, Storj, and others it would be a great way to get some strong alliances in the industry. 

{Manifestations}
I futjrcat will see this through.

{Funding}
Any media i can handle. 
Just vote! 

{The Shelter's Commitment to the DAO}
The CHIS is interested in staking as well so we'll get them set up to do that if  their holdings become enough. 

SHELTER ADDRESS : 0x17ab2562651c724E5F4cD55472aa41Ee0f203ED7

{Misc}
Feel free to drop anything you think pertinent to your proposal here

I futjr hereby swear to this proposal as being thoughtout, derived from a desire to succeed, and for my fellow felines. I also understand that once this proposal runs its course I cannot propose this shelter for another 6 months and will redelegate my stake after the period of vote is over.
choices: I will not delegate to CIHS
